Comment: This is the only time you'll see me playing Nb3 instead of Nc2 in this opening variation, only when the Black Bishop posts at c5. Otherwise, I prefer to keep my Knight a step closer to the center. However, the gain of tempo in this case justifies the temporary misplacing of the Knight.
